WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 22=

00:01:40.980 --> 00:01:41.820 line:80%
Mr. Zhou.

00:01:43.420 --> 00:01:44.290 line:80%
How did you know...

00:02:07.210 --> 00:02:08.050 line:80%
Mr. Zhou,

00:02:08.780 --> 00:02:09.620 line:80%
please sit.

00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:24.650 line:80%
Mr. Zhou,

00:02:24.930 --> 00:02:25.970 line:80%
have some tea.

00:02:31.370 --> 00:02:32.410 line:80%
May I ask

00:02:33.140 --> 00:02:35.060 line:80%
what troubles you so deeply?

00:02:38.210 --> 00:02:39.410 line:80%
I have a sworn sister.

00:02:40.460 --> 00:02:42.360 line:80%
When she was little,
her family fell into ruin.

00:02:43.650 --> 00:02:45.140 line:80%
Her father and brothers were foolish.

00:02:45.140 --> 00:02:46.620 line:80%
Her stepmother was cruel.

00:02:46.620 --> 00:02:49.140 line:80%
So, she sought refuge
in my home at a young age.

00:02:51.650 --> 00:02:53.900 line:80%
We grew up eating and living together,

00:02:53.900 --> 00:02:55.090 line:80%
playing and laughing.

00:02:56.090 --> 00:02:58.580 line:80%
We had so much fun.

00:02:58.580 --> 00:03:00.620 line:80%
I thought that when we grew up,
I'd marry her.

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:02.930 line:80%
But when I was 12,

00:03:04.650 --> 00:03:07.090 line:80%
my father suddenly arranged
a marriage for me.

00:03:07.635 --> 00:03:09.095 line:80%
Then my grandmother ordered my sister

00:03:09.106 --> 00:03:10.410 line:80%
to move out of my courtyard.

00:03:10.410 --> 00:03:12.340 line:80%
We were no longer allowed to be close.

00:03:13.620 --> 00:03:14.530 line:80%
Are you dissatisfied

00:03:15.580 --> 00:03:17.020 line:80%
with this betrothal?

00:03:17.020 --> 00:03:17.860 line:80%
I don't know.

00:03:18.530 --> 00:03:20.060 line:80%
The family I'm betrothed to

00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:22.020 line:80%
is a long-standing match for ours.

00:03:22.810 --> 00:03:24.223 line:80%
My future father- and mother-in-law

00:03:24.234 --> 00:03:25.460 line:80%
are kind and sensible people.

00:03:27.460 --> 00:03:29.060 line:80%
The girl I'm engaged to

00:03:30.090 --> 00:03:31.060 line:80%
is very good.

00:03:31.580 --> 00:03:32.460 line:80%
Very good.

00:03:34.650 --> 00:03:35.530 line:80%
My mother says

00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:37.740 line:80%
that as long as I marry her,

00:03:38.900 --> 00:03:40.690 line:80%
I can secure my future position.

00:03:43.580 --> 00:03:44.740 line:80%
No one would dare object.

00:03:45.090 --> 00:03:46.370 line:80%
So, Mr. Zhou,

00:03:47.180 --> 00:03:48.140 line:80%
does the position matter

00:03:48.930 --> 00:03:49.770 line:80%
to you?

00:03:49.970 --> 00:03:51.410 line:80%
I don't care about that.

00:03:51.570 --> 00:03:52.860 line:80%
I'd rather live freely,

00:03:52.880 --> 00:03:54.140 line:80%
drifting across the rivers.

00:03:54.140 --> 00:03:55.490 line:80%
So, to you,

00:03:55.490 --> 00:03:57.300 line:80%
between your sister and your fiancée,

00:03:57.300 --> 00:03:58.970 line:80%
who can't live without you?

00:04:01.970 --> 00:04:02.810 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:04:03.030 --> 00:04:05.060 line:80%
I'm not ready to marry yet.

00:04:05.060 --> 00:04:06.740 line:80%
Do you wish to postpone it,

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:08.370 line:80%
or do you not wish to marry me at all?

00:04:08.370 --> 00:04:10.210 line:80%
I don't wish

00:04:10.210 --> 00:04:11.410 line:80%
to rush into marriage.

00:04:17.410 --> 00:04:18.410 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:04:19.580 --> 00:04:20.420 line:80%
I won't marry.

00:04:21.290 --> 00:04:22.303 line:80%
If that day truly comes,

00:04:23.940 --> 00:04:25.020 line:80%
I'll become a nun.

00:04:29.410 --> 00:04:30.850 line:80%
The girl I'm engaged to

00:04:32.970 --> 00:04:33.940 line:80%
is clever,

00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:35.380 line:80%
beautiful,

00:04:36.140 --> 00:04:37.340 line:80%
and capable.

00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:40.580 line:80%
Even without me,

00:04:42.820 --> 00:04:45.340 line:80%
she'll surely find a better match.

00:04:48.090 --> 00:04:49.780 line:80%
But if my sister loses me,

00:04:51.170 --> 00:04:52.850 line:80%
she'll have no way to survive.

00:04:53.700 --> 00:04:54.700 line:80%
Isn't that the answer?

00:04:55.820 --> 00:04:57.650 line:80%
The futures and happiness

00:04:58.210 --> 00:04:59.460 line:80%
of the three people

00:05:00.340 --> 00:05:02.530 line:80%
depend on your choice alone.

00:05:03.410 --> 00:05:04.940 line:80%
You should decide soon.

00:05:11.210 --> 00:05:12.050 line:80%
Here.

00:05:13.460 --> 00:05:14.700 line:80%
The weather is dry.

00:05:15.580 --> 00:05:16.850 line:80%
Your breath is unsteady.

00:05:17.780 --> 00:05:18.746 line:80%
Have more tea.

00:05:20.650 --> 00:05:21.730 line:80%
Thank you, sir.

00:05:41.140 --> 00:05:42.410 line:80%
You are right.

00:05:42.410 --> 00:05:43.460 line:80%
I should decide soon.

00:06:00.686 --> 00:06:01.786 line:80%
What did you put in the tea?

00:06:02.850 --> 00:06:05.020 line:80%
It's called the Coward's Courage.

00:06:05.020 --> 00:06:06.580 line:80%
It makes one's blood surge,

00:06:06.580 --> 00:06:07.909 line:80%
filling the heart with ambition,

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:08.940 line:80%
itching to fight at once.

00:06:09.730 --> 00:06:11.140 line:80%
The Young Lord Zhou

00:06:11.140 --> 00:06:12.090 line:80%
needs

00:06:12.090 --> 00:06:13.460 line:80%
a little courage right now.

00:06:39.970 --> 00:06:40.810 line:80%
Yours.

00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:43.690 line:80%
- Yours.
- Thanks.

00:06:44.500 --> 00:06:45.340 line:80%
Yours.

00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:48.210 line:80%
And yours.

00:06:50.970 --> 00:06:51.970 line:80%
Thank you, sir.

00:07:03.380 --> 00:07:04.650 line:80%
You want to marry someone else?

00:07:05.780 --> 00:07:06.780 line:80%
Over my dead body.

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:28.460 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:30.780 --> 00:07:31.900 line:80%
Zhuo and I

00:07:31.900 --> 00:07:33.650 line:80%
did something big for you today.

00:07:33.977 --> 00:07:35.548 line:80%
The mosquito balm samples has arrived.

00:07:35.559 --> 00:07:36.399 line:80%
Over there.

00:07:37.210 --> 00:07:38.740 line:80%
Really? I'll go take a look.

00:07:40.940 --> 00:07:41.780 line:80%
Zhao.

00:07:42.170 --> 00:07:43.090 line:80%
Yuqi.

00:07:45.940 --> 00:07:46.900 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:07:48.090 --> 00:07:48.930 line:80%
what are you doing?

00:07:51.820 --> 00:07:52.780 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:52.780 --> 00:07:53.650 line:80%
we need to talk.

00:07:54.386 --> 00:07:55.605 line:80%
I wish to cancel our betrothal.

00:07:55.730 --> 00:07:56.570 line:80%
Cancel?

00:07:57.140 --> 00:07:57.980 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:58.170 --> 00:07:59.010 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:07:59.460 --> 00:08:01.580 line:80%
This thought has been
in my heart for years.

00:08:01.580 --> 00:08:02.686 line:80%
You are exceptional

00:08:02.697 --> 00:08:03.693 line:80%
in talent and appearance.

00:08:04.530 --> 00:08:05.650 line:80%
I'm mediocre.

00:08:06.650 --> 00:08:07.780 line:80%
I truly don't deserve you.

00:08:08.210 --> 00:08:09.140 line:80%
Why exactly?

00:08:09.850 --> 00:08:11.290 line:80%
All these years in sparring,

00:08:11.290 --> 00:08:12.730 line:80%
you knocked me down every time.

00:08:13.200 --> 00:08:14.700 line:80%
My martial arts are inferior to yours.

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:15.970 line:80%
I'm not as decisive as you.

00:08:15.970 --> 00:08:17.380 line:80%
You surpass me in every way.

00:08:17.380 --> 00:08:19.500 line:80%
But I don't want a wife
who is stronger than I am.

00:08:19.500 --> 00:08:20.580 line:80%
I hope my wife

00:08:22.050 --> 00:08:22.970 line:80%
is understanding,

00:08:23.610 --> 00:08:24.700 line:80%
gentle, and virtuous.

00:08:24.700 --> 00:08:26.500 line:80%
Why not just say Min Xinrou's name?

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:27.970 line:80%
I do care for Xinrou.

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:32.980 line:80%
That's a rat.

00:08:33.980 --> 00:08:35.410 line:80%
What is going on?

00:08:35.410 --> 00:08:36.740 line:80%
I'm not holding a blade

00:08:36.740 --> 00:08:38.620 line:80%
to your throat to force you to marry.

00:08:38.620 --> 00:08:39.980 line:80%
Even if you held a blade to me,

00:08:40.282 --> 00:08:41.615 line:80%
I'd still break off the betrothal.

00:08:41.780 --> 00:08:42.620 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi,

00:08:43.780 --> 00:08:44.620 line:80%
have you

00:08:45.330 --> 00:08:46.620 line:80%
thought this through?

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:47.500 line:80%
I have.

00:08:50.220 --> 00:08:51.060 line:80%
Zhao,

00:08:51.690 --> 00:08:53.220 line:80%
I beg you to let me go.

00:09:02.620 --> 00:09:03.460 line:80%
Very well.

00:09:04.620 --> 00:09:05.930 line:80%
Since you have decided,

00:09:06.980 --> 00:09:08.140 line:80%
the betrothal

00:09:09.650 --> 00:09:11.020 line:80%
is hereby canceled.

00:09:17.330 --> 00:09:18.170 line:80%
Please leave.

00:09:20.450 --> 00:09:21.930 line:80%
Thanks for granting it, Zhao.

00:09:26.330 --> 00:09:28.700 line:80%
I'll beat this heartless man to death.

00:09:28.710 --> 00:09:29.570 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:30.810 line:80%
You...

00:09:30.810 --> 00:09:31.650 line:80%
Calm down.

00:09:32.170 --> 00:09:34.170 line:80%
This is intolerable.

00:09:39.050 --> 00:09:39.890 line:80%
Young Master,

00:09:40.690 --> 00:09:42.530 line:80%
I'll spread the news of Zhou Yuqi

00:09:42.530 --> 00:09:43.650 line:80%
canceling the betrothal.

00:09:43.650 --> 00:09:45.170 line:80%
I guarantee the entire town

00:09:45.690 --> 00:09:46.740 line:80%
and the whole Jianghu

00:09:47.500 --> 00:09:48.620 line:80%
will know.

00:09:51.860 --> 00:09:55.540 line:80%
(Kind and Hospitable)

00:10:05.650 --> 00:10:07.140 line:80%
Were we not returning to Qingque Sect?

00:10:07.620 --> 00:10:08.900 line:80%
Why is everyone staring at me?

00:10:12.066 --> 00:10:13.259 line:80%
The betrothal is truly broken?

00:10:16.570 --> 00:10:17.410 line:80%
Zhuo,

00:10:17.810 --> 00:10:18.930 line:80%
how did you know?

00:10:18.930 --> 00:10:20.380 line:80%
The whole town knows.

00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:22.810 line:80%
They say Young Lord Zhou knelt

00:10:22.810 --> 00:10:24.730 line:80%
and begged you to spare him.

00:10:24.730 --> 00:10:25.570 line:80%
He was always

00:10:25.570 --> 00:10:27.330 line:80%
so attentive and considerate toward you.

00:10:27.330 --> 00:10:28.690 line:80%
How could he suddenly break it off?

00:10:29.140 --> 00:10:30.570 line:80%
Did you do something

00:10:30.570 --> 00:10:31.620 line:80%
that frightened him?

00:10:31.620 --> 00:10:32.930 line:80%
You are making things up.

00:10:32.930 --> 00:10:34.450 line:80%
We parted on good terms.

00:10:34.450 --> 00:10:36.070 line:80%
If you don't believe me, ask him.

00:10:36.140 --> 00:10:37.570 line:80%
I went to find Zhou Yuqi.

00:10:37.570 --> 00:10:38.650 line:80%
He is not in his room.

00:10:39.100 --> 00:10:39.940 line:80%
Perhaps

00:10:40.500 --> 00:10:41.500 line:80%
he went for a walk.

00:10:43.530 --> 00:10:45.170 line:80%
Are you asking about Mr. Zhou?

00:10:46.170 --> 00:10:47.100 line:80%
Early this morning,

00:10:47.100 --> 00:10:48.620 line:80%
he boarded a carriage with a young lady

00:10:48.620 --> 00:10:49.460 line:80%
and already left.

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:51.050 line:80%
He said he'd inform the elders.

00:10:52.900 --> 00:10:53.740 line:80%
Men

00:10:56.650 --> 00:10:58.020 line:80%
are indeed all worthless.

00:11:14.780 --> 00:11:15.620 line:80%
You all eat first.

00:11:15.930 --> 00:11:17.140 line:80%
I'll go for a walk.

00:11:18.500 --> 00:11:19.740 line:80%
You are not eating at all?

00:11:27.740 --> 00:11:29.530 line:80%
Xingjia truly has a big mouth.

00:11:33.690 --> 00:11:34.530 line:80%
That is not right.

00:11:35.170 --> 00:11:36.860 line:80%
He was with me the whole time.

00:11:49.290 --> 00:11:50.130 line:80%
Zhao, you're here.

00:11:52.570 --> 00:11:53.570 line:80%
Was it you who spread

00:11:53.570 --> 00:11:54.980 line:80%
the news of my broken betrothal?

00:11:54.980 --> 00:11:56.810 line:80%
I merely made a choice for you.

00:11:57.500 --> 00:11:58.530 line:80%
You're so clever.

00:11:59.100 --> 00:12:00.330 line:80%
You did not like Mr. Zhou

00:12:00.330 --> 00:12:01.380 line:80%
and did not wish to marry.

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:03.020 line:80%
You hinted at me several times

00:12:03.380 --> 00:12:04.860 line:80%
to push him a little.

00:12:05.570 --> 00:12:07.980 line:80%
I only went along with the flow

00:12:07.980 --> 00:12:08.980 line:80%
to fulfill your wish.

00:12:08.980 --> 00:12:10.170 line:80%
It benefits all sides.

00:12:10.170 --> 00:12:11.170 line:80%
Why not?

00:12:11.244 --> 00:12:12.748 line:80%
How do you know that I don't like him

00:12:12.759 --> 00:12:13.849 line:80%
and don't wish to marry him?

00:12:13.860 --> 00:12:14.839 line:80%
Do you like the splendor

00:12:14.850 --> 00:12:16.930 line:80%
and wealth of Peiqiong Manor

00:12:16.930 --> 00:12:19.220 line:80%
or Mr. Zhou's thoughtfulness?

00:12:19.980 --> 00:12:20.820 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:12:21.170 --> 00:12:22.643 line:80%
you're not even as good as Zhou Yuqi.

00:12:23.330 --> 00:12:25.330 line:80%
At least he truly wishes
to marry Min Xinrou.

00:12:26.140 --> 00:12:28.530 line:80%
But you don't even know what you want.

00:12:28.530 --> 00:12:29.370 line:80%
Shut up.

00:12:30.900 --> 00:12:32.900 line:80%
There is no Zhou Yuqi in your heart.

00:12:33.530 --> 00:12:34.620 line:80%
There is only me.

00:12:35.650 --> 00:12:37.290 line:80%
You simply dare not admit it.

00:12:41.380 --> 00:12:43.100 line:80%
Don't flatter yourself.

00:12:43.820 --> 00:12:44.690 line:80%
You can like anyone

00:12:44.690 --> 00:12:45.900 line:80%
as you please.

00:12:45.900 --> 00:12:47.410 line:80%
We'll go our separate ways.

00:12:47.410 --> 00:12:48.780 line:80%
May we never meet again.

00:12:49.740 --> 00:12:50.873 line:80%
I heard Hexagonal Persimmons

00:12:50.884 --> 00:12:52.890 line:80%
are mostly produced
in the southeast three states.

00:12:53.290 --> 00:12:56.020 line:80%
I must find the Shi brothers.

00:12:56.020 --> 00:12:57.140 line:80%
But how?

00:12:58.100 --> 00:13:00.330 line:80%
I can only send out all my followers

00:13:00.690 --> 00:13:02.330 line:80%
to make a grand search

00:13:02.330 --> 00:13:04.980 line:80%
and turn the three states upside down.

00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:06.460 line:80%
Besides,

00:13:07.290 --> 00:13:08.570 line:80%
many people in Jianghu

00:13:09.100 --> 00:13:10.140 line:80%
are eager

00:13:10.140 --> 00:13:11.740 line:80%
to find the Shi brothers.

00:13:12.570 --> 00:13:14.380 line:80%
If I spread the news...

00:13:14.380 --> 00:13:15.220 line:80%
Don't you dare.

00:13:17.860 --> 00:13:19.330 line:80%
So, you turned back after all.

00:13:21.780 --> 00:13:22.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:13:24.980 --> 00:13:27.020 line:80%
Young Lord Zhou and Miss Min are back.

00:13:29.500 --> 00:13:30.340 line:80%
Zhao?

00:13:45.530 --> 00:13:46.370 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:13:46.930 --> 00:13:47.686 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:13:47.697 --> 00:13:48.860 line:80%
I did not try to harm myself.

00:13:48.860 --> 00:13:50.140 line:80%
I did not become a nun.

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:51.530 line:80%
I just went out to clear my head.

00:13:52.020 --> 00:13:53.450 line:80%
Please don't worry.

00:13:54.290 --> 00:13:56.220 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi and I decided
to cancel the betrothal.

00:13:56.900 --> 00:13:58.330 line:80%
Don't give him a hard time.

00:13:59.100 --> 00:14:01.220 line:80%
(From Cai Zhao)

00:14:05.420 --> 00:14:06.280 line:80%
Everything

00:14:06.280 --> 00:14:07.650 line:80%
is all my fault.

00:14:07.650 --> 00:14:08.780 line:80%
Don't hurt Yuqi.

00:14:09.330 --> 00:14:11.220 line:80%
We've wronged Zhao,

00:14:11.220 --> 00:14:12.810 line:80%
so we came back

00:14:12.810 --> 00:14:14.113 line:80%
to apologize to her.

00:14:14.124 --> 00:14:15.782 line:80%
What's the use of that?
He deserves this.

00:14:15.793 --> 00:14:16.980 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:14:16.980 --> 00:14:18.170 line:80%
We should cherish beauty.

00:14:18.980 --> 00:14:20.500 line:80%
Talk it out properly.

00:14:23.450 --> 00:14:24.290 line:80%
Yuqi,

00:14:24.620 --> 00:14:25.460 line:80%
are you alright?

00:14:28.450 --> 00:14:29.330 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:31.170 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:14:31.530 --> 00:14:32.620 line:80%
That is good.

00:14:37.450 --> 00:14:38.290 line:80%
Yuqi!

00:14:38.500 --> 00:14:40.140 line:80%
Zhao suffered so much grievance.

00:14:40.140 --> 00:14:41.380 line:80%
A single apology is enough?

00:14:46.410 --> 00:14:47.650 line:80%
I alone bear the consequences.

00:14:48.170 --> 00:14:49.020 line:80%
All faults

00:14:49.020 --> 00:14:49.900 line:80%
are mine.

00:14:50.170 --> 00:14:51.140 line:80%
Beat me to death.

00:14:51.650 --> 00:14:52.500 line:80%
I won't regret it.

00:14:59.860 --> 00:15:01.780 line:80%
Don't hit my Yuqi.

00:15:01.780 --> 00:15:03.650 line:80%
Don't ruin his peerless face.

00:15:04.839 --> 00:15:06.079 line:80%
You came to beat me too, right?

00:15:11.340 --> 00:15:12.340 line:80%
(From Cai Zhao)

00:15:14.050 --> 00:15:16.650 line:80%
Zhao only said
she went out to clear her head.

00:15:16.650 --> 00:15:18.980 line:80%
It does not mean she left with Mr. Mu.

00:15:18.980 --> 00:15:20.810 line:80%
The innkeeper told me

00:15:20.810 --> 00:15:22.220 line:80%
that Master You came earlier

00:15:22.220 --> 00:15:24.500 line:80%
and packed up everything
from Zhao's room.

00:15:25.570 --> 00:15:26.410 line:80%
He said

00:15:26.980 --> 00:15:28.220 line:80%
she might need them.

00:15:28.530 --> 00:15:30.170 line:80%
I knew you were hiding something.

00:15:30.620 --> 00:15:32.500 line:80%
Did Cai Zhao elope with Mu Qingyan?

00:15:32.500 --> 00:15:33.930 line:80%
What eloping?

00:15:33.930 --> 00:15:35.170 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.

00:15:35.170 --> 00:15:37.042 line:80%
Zhao was only upset

00:15:37.053 --> 00:15:38.380 line:80%
and went out to clear her head.

00:15:38.380 --> 00:15:39.380 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:15:39.380 --> 00:15:41.330 line:80%
I've been watching the demonic sect.

00:15:41.330 --> 00:15:43.220 line:80%
This morning,

00:15:43.220 --> 00:15:45.050 line:80%
they suddenly withdrew from the town.

00:15:45.050 --> 00:15:46.780 line:80%
Zhao happened to go out
at the same time.

00:15:47.570 --> 00:15:48.450 line:80%
Could it be

00:15:49.170 --> 00:15:50.930 line:80%
just a coincidence?

00:15:50.930 --> 00:15:51.770 line:80%
Yes.

00:15:51.920 --> 00:15:53.246 line:80%
That's too much of a coincidence.

00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:55.140 line:80%
Though Zhou Yuqi is no good,

00:15:55.980 --> 00:15:57.380 line:80%
if Cai Zhao therefore

00:15:57.380 --> 00:15:59.100 line:80%
colludes with the demonic sect,

00:15:59.100 --> 00:16:00.740 line:80%
the crime would be even worse.

00:16:02.380 --> 00:16:03.220 line:80%
Remember:

00:16:03.780 --> 00:16:05.690 line:80%
Zhao only went out to clear her head.

00:16:05.690 --> 00:16:07.450 line:80%
She has nothing to do
with the demonic sect.

00:16:07.450 --> 00:16:09.140 line:80%
Song Yuzhi, what's wrong with you?

00:16:09.140 --> 00:16:11.140 line:80%
First,, you cooperated with Mu Qingyan.

00:16:11.140 --> 00:16:12.720 line:80%
Now, you openly shield Cai Zhao.

00:16:12.731 --> 00:16:14.505 line:80%
Have you lost your sense
of right and wrong?

00:16:14.516 --> 00:16:15.753 line:80%
Master will arrive in two days.

00:16:16.140 --> 00:16:17.020 line:80%
No matter what,

00:16:17.020 --> 00:16:18.690 line:80%
we'll meet him first.

00:16:19.780 --> 00:16:21.690 line:80%
Besides, Nie Zhe may be nearby.

00:16:22.020 --> 00:16:22.860 line:80%
Danger is everywhere.

00:16:24.380 --> 00:16:25.260 line:80%
The priority

00:16:25.260 --> 00:16:26.650 line:80%
is to find Zhao first,

00:16:26.650 --> 00:16:27.690 line:80%
in case something happens.

00:16:29.900 --> 00:16:32.140 line:80%
Elder Hu has been locked
in Bliss Palace,

00:16:32.140 --> 00:16:33.570 line:80%
guarded by Shangguan Haonan.

00:16:34.170 --> 00:16:35.033 line:80%
What about Mu Qingyan?

00:16:35.044 --> 00:16:36.306 line:80%
He hasn't returned to the sect.

00:16:36.317 --> 00:16:38.290 line:80%
I heard he left with Cai Zhao.

00:16:38.940 --> 00:16:39.810 line:80%
You may go.

00:16:39.810 --> 00:16:40.650 line:80%
Yes.

00:16:43.380 --> 00:16:45.930 line:80%
Mu Qingyan indeed has some ability.

00:16:45.930 --> 00:16:47.860 line:80%
He even colluded with the Six Sects.

00:16:48.450 --> 00:16:49.290 line:80%
Cai Zhao

00:16:50.450 --> 00:16:51.410 line:80%
can't be left alive.

00:16:51.860 --> 00:16:52.810 line:80%
Rest assured, Chief.

00:16:54.740 --> 00:16:56.170 line:80%
I'll send someone at once.

00:17:00.050 --> 00:17:01.650 line:80%
Sending Hu Fengge

00:17:01.650 --> 00:17:03.650 line:80%
was not enough for Mu Qingyan?

00:17:03.650 --> 00:17:05.180 line:80%
You want to send more?

00:17:08.980 --> 00:17:10.740 line:80%
This time, you need not act.

00:17:11.980 --> 00:17:13.460 line:80%
Just wait to collect

00:17:13.980 --> 00:17:14.890 line:80%
Mu Qingyan's corpse.

00:17:15.220 --> 00:17:16.060 line:80%
Yes.

00:17:22.789 --> 00:17:24.676 line:80%
This is the map
of the southeast three states.

00:17:25.330 --> 00:17:26.330 line:80%
We start here

00:17:26.810 --> 00:17:28.740 line:80%
and follow this road all the way.

00:17:29.330 --> 00:17:30.760 line:80%
Places that produce persimmons

00:17:30.771 --> 00:17:32.220 line:80%
must have fertile land and people.

00:17:32.220 --> 00:17:33.660 line:80%
The villages and towns along the way

00:17:33.660 --> 00:17:35.370 line:80%
should all be searched.

00:17:35.370 --> 00:17:36.530 line:80%
Zhao, do you know

00:17:36.530 --> 00:17:37.740 line:80%
how vast

00:17:38.060 --> 00:17:39.280 line:80%
the southeast three states are?

00:17:43.780 --> 00:17:44.740 line:80%
It seems

00:17:45.740 --> 00:17:46.580 line:80%
quite large.

00:17:46.890 --> 00:17:48.090 line:80%
Within those states,

00:17:48.530 --> 00:17:50.660 line:80%
how many villages and towns are there?

00:17:59.220 --> 00:18:00.460 line:80%
Only a few hundred.

00:18:04.420 --> 00:18:05.290 line:80%
Right now, we have

00:18:05.290 --> 00:18:06.883 line:80%
only the Hexagonal Persimmons as a clue.

00:18:07.130 --> 00:18:08.130 line:80%
What else can we do?

00:18:08.610 --> 00:18:10.500 line:80%
Do you have a better idea?

00:18:10.780 --> 00:18:11.620 line:80%
No.

00:18:14.460 --> 00:18:15.530 line:80%
I'll follow you.

00:18:31.180 --> 00:18:32.020 line:80%
Let's go.

00:18:32.890 --> 00:18:33.940 line:80%
My legs are numb.

00:19:29.090 --> 00:19:30.290 line:80%
After crossing that mountain,

00:19:30.290 --> 00:19:31.980 line:80%
we should reach the next village.

00:19:31.980 --> 00:19:32.820 line:80%
If we had just

00:19:33.570 --> 00:19:34.850 line:80%
crossed the river earlier,

00:19:35.646 --> 00:19:36.846 line:80%
would it not have been faster?

00:19:39.890 --> 00:19:41.070 line:80%
Didn't you hear the villagers?

00:19:41.780 --> 00:19:43.020 line:80%
The heavy rain these days

00:19:43.020 --> 00:19:43.980 line:80%
washed away the bridge.

00:19:44.980 --> 00:19:46.493 line:80%
Climbing the mountain is the shortcut.

00:20:44.850 --> 00:20:46.420 line:80%
Cooperating with Mu Qingyan

00:20:46.740 --> 00:20:48.130 line:80%
was solely my decision.

00:20:48.570 --> 00:20:50.020 line:80%
I'm willing to accept punishment.

00:20:50.020 --> 00:20:51.020 line:80%
- You...
- Master.

00:20:57.890 --> 00:20:58.730 line:80%
Forget it.

00:20:58.980 --> 00:20:59.850 line:80%
I'm also at fault.

00:21:01.700 --> 00:21:04.330 line:80%
I've been so protective of you

00:21:04.890 --> 00:21:07.050 line:80%
that you don't know
how dangerous Jianghu is.

00:21:08.090 --> 00:21:08.930 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:21:09.460 --> 00:21:10.370 line:80%
answer me.

00:21:10.740 --> 00:21:12.740 line:80%
Do you truly think Mu Qingyan

00:21:13.130 --> 00:21:14.050 line:80%
is a good person?

00:21:16.220 --> 00:21:17.060 line:80%
He...

00:21:18.220 --> 00:21:19.220 line:80%
He's never done evil.

00:21:19.220 --> 00:21:20.500 line:80%
That is in public.

00:21:20.500 --> 00:21:21.460 line:80%
What about in private?

00:21:21.893 --> 00:21:23.149 line:80%
The identity of the man in black

00:21:23.160 --> 00:21:24.180 line:80%
is still a mystery.

00:21:24.810 --> 00:21:25.980 line:80%
You believe

00:21:25.980 --> 00:21:27.780 line:80%
he is the one who massacred
the Chang clan.

00:21:28.180 --> 00:21:30.570 line:80%
But that's only Mu Qingyan's story.

00:21:30.570 --> 00:21:32.020 line:80%
You've been to the fort.

00:21:32.020 --> 00:21:33.740 line:80%
You should know its mechanisms

00:21:33.740 --> 00:21:35.090 line:80%
are unparalleled in the world.

00:21:35.090 --> 00:21:37.530 line:80%
To break them, there is only one way:

00:21:37.530 --> 00:21:39.850 line:80%
working from someone inside.

00:21:40.530 --> 00:21:41.660 line:80%
Are you saying...?

00:21:41.980 --> 00:21:43.330 line:80%
Chang was honest and kind.

00:21:44.090 --> 00:21:45.810 line:80%
He likely let a wolf into the house.

00:21:46.330 --> 00:21:47.170 line:80%
Master, you're right.

00:21:47.610 --> 00:21:48.656 line:80%
People of the demonic sect

00:21:48.700 --> 00:21:49.540 line:80%
can never be trusted.

00:21:50.420 --> 00:21:52.090 line:80%
Mu Qingyan disguised himself
as Chang Ning

00:21:52.090 --> 00:21:53.220 line:80%
and infiltrated Qingque Sect.

00:21:53.587 --> 00:21:55.733 line:80%
His ambition is vicious
and not to be underestimated.

00:21:57.740 --> 00:21:58.580 line:80%
Master,

00:21:59.420 --> 00:22:00.460 line:80%
could Zhao

00:22:01.420 --> 00:22:03.420 line:80%
have been taken by Mu Qingyan?

00:22:03.420 --> 00:22:04.330 line:80%
Even if she was taken,

00:22:04.780 --> 00:22:06.753 line:80%
she only has herself to blame
for misjudging him.

00:22:07.610 --> 00:22:08.810 line:80%
This matter is serious.

00:22:09.610 --> 00:22:10.700 line:80%
Don't spread it publicly.

00:22:11.180 --> 00:22:13.220 line:80%
Just say she went wandering

00:22:13.220 --> 00:22:14.570 line:80%
to clear her mind.

00:22:15.290 --> 00:22:17.530 line:80%
You will investigate in secret.

00:22:17.530 --> 00:22:18.570 line:80%
If you find

00:22:18.570 --> 00:22:20.740 line:80%
any demonic villains harassing her,

00:22:20.740 --> 00:22:22.090 line:80%
kill them without mercy.

00:22:22.090 --> 00:22:22.930 line:80%
Yes.

00:22:33.850 --> 00:22:34.690 line:80%
Hungry?

00:22:36.940 --> 00:22:38.330 line:80%
Out traveling,

00:22:38.810 --> 00:22:40.020 line:80%
and still so particular.

00:23:00.130 --> 00:23:01.500 line:80%
It'll rain soon.

00:23:03.290 --> 00:23:05.050 line:80%
Let's find a place
to take shelter later.

00:23:07.570 --> 00:23:08.410 line:80%
Alright.

00:23:53.500 --> 00:23:55.290 line:80%
When can I tell you how much I miss you

00:23:56.090 --> 00:23:57.780 line:80%
during the rain?

00:23:58.180 --> 00:23:59.500 line:80%
In the past, I did not like rain.

00:24:00.460 --> 00:24:01.610 line:80%
It felt damp and unpleasant.

00:24:03.130 --> 00:24:03.970 line:80%
But today,

00:24:04.530 --> 00:24:05.570 line:80%
I find it

00:24:07.130 --> 00:24:07.970 line:80%
quite nice.

00:24:10.826 --> 00:24:12.479 line:80%
The road will be slippery
after the rain.

00:24:12.940 --> 00:24:14.020 line:80%
It seems we must

00:24:14.020 --> 00:24:15.290 line:80%
stay here one more day.

00:24:16.570 --> 00:24:17.410 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:24:18.500 --> 00:24:19.980 line:80%
Since we're staying another day,

00:24:19.980 --> 00:24:21.610 line:80%
I'll gather more firewood.

00:24:26.220 --> 00:24:27.260 line:80%
(What's wrong with him?)

00:24:27.610 --> 00:24:29.020 line:80%
(More calm than I am.)

00:25:14.130 --> 00:25:15.700 line:80%
There may be wild beasts at night.

00:25:16.330 --> 00:25:17.890 line:80%
I'll keep watch tonight.

00:26:33.610 --> 00:26:34.460 line:80%
If

00:26:36.020 --> 00:26:37.780 line:80%
we could always stay like this,

00:26:38.660 --> 00:26:39.610 line:80%
roaming Jianghu,

00:26:40.810 --> 00:26:41.660 line:80%
seeing the world,

00:26:44.660 --> 00:26:46.370 line:80%
would that not be a beautiful thing?

00:26:53.420 --> 00:26:54.420 line:80%
It would.

00:27:34.940 --> 00:27:35.780 line:80%
Zhao,

00:27:36.220 --> 00:27:37.420 line:80%
are you sure the Shi brothers

00:27:38.130 --> 00:27:39.050 line:80%
are nearby?

00:27:39.700 --> 00:27:41.180 line:80%
When I was little,

00:27:41.180 --> 00:27:42.633 line:80%
I ate this kind of persimmon cake.

00:27:43.290 --> 00:27:44.660 line:80%
They've secluded themselves

00:27:44.660 --> 00:27:46.220 line:80%
in a very distant place.

00:27:47.090 --> 00:27:48.420 line:80%
But the water we drink

00:27:49.660 --> 00:27:50.980 line:80%
comes from the same river.

00:27:52.890 --> 00:27:53.863 line:80%
Within the three states,

00:27:54.180 --> 00:27:55.500 line:80%
only this Su River

00:27:55.500 --> 00:27:57.500 line:80%
connects to Qingluo River
of Luoying Valley.

00:27:58.050 --> 00:27:58.890 line:80%
However,

00:27:59.220 --> 00:28:01.530 line:80%
there are dozens of towns
along this river.

00:28:01.530 --> 00:28:02.780 line:80%
If we search one by one...

00:28:02.780 --> 00:28:03.620 line:80%
No need.

00:28:03.940 --> 00:28:04.920 line:80%
We only need to buy

00:28:04.931 --> 00:28:06.357 line:80%
the persimmon cakes from each place.

00:28:07.700 --> 00:28:09.090 line:80%
Once we find the same taste,

00:28:09.780 --> 00:28:10.890 line:80%
we'll know

00:28:10.890 --> 00:28:12.740 line:80%
where Uncle Shi is living in seclusion.

00:28:43.020 --> 00:28:43.860 line:80%
The taste is close.

00:28:44.130 --> 00:28:45.043 line:80%
They should be nearby.

00:28:45.320 --> 00:28:46.180 line:80%
Buy more.

00:28:46.180 --> 00:28:47.260 line:80%
I can eat ten more.

00:28:47.460 --> 00:28:48.300 line:80%
Zhao,

00:28:49.020 --> 00:28:50.810 line:80%
why not try again tomorrow?

00:28:51.720 --> 00:28:52.570 line:80%
No.

00:28:52.570 --> 00:28:53.420 line:80%
We must hurry.

00:29:03.290 --> 00:29:04.130 line:80%
Don't move.

00:29:04.599 --> 00:29:05.832 line:80%
Persimmons are cold in nature.

00:29:06.220 --> 00:29:07.280 line:80%
They've hurt your stomach.

00:29:07.740 --> 00:29:09.890 line:80%
I just used my inner power
to clear your meridians.

00:29:10.290 --> 00:29:11.610 line:80%
Your inner power is unstable.

00:29:12.330 --> 00:29:13.330 line:80%
If you keep eating,

00:29:13.610 --> 00:29:15.330 line:80%
you may have diarrhea tonight.

00:29:15.330 --> 00:29:16.170 line:80%
Diarrhea?

00:29:19.500 --> 00:29:21.130 line:80%
You know quite a bit about medicine.

00:29:21.890 --> 00:29:22.890 line:80%
Father read widely.

00:29:24.130 --> 00:29:25.460 line:80%
I read many of his books.

00:29:28.220 --> 00:29:30.420 line:80%
He only wished to leave
the Hanhai Mountains

00:29:31.500 --> 00:29:32.613 line:80%
and stay away from Jianghu,

00:29:33.700 --> 00:29:35.500 line:80%
so he learned many ways
to make a living.

00:29:36.980 --> 00:29:38.460 line:80%
He once wanted to be a physician,

00:29:38.890 --> 00:29:39.980 line:80%
journeying across the world,

00:29:41.130 --> 00:29:41.970 line:80%
healing the sick.

00:29:42.220 --> 00:29:44.500 line:80%
So, we had many medical books.

00:29:53.850 --> 00:29:55.870 line:80%
Small trinkets!

00:29:56.330 --> 00:29:57.220 line:80%
I've inquired already.

00:29:57.220 --> 00:29:58.070 line:80%
Take a look.

00:29:58.080 --> 00:29:59.130 line:80%
People in the neighborhood

00:29:59.740 --> 00:30:01.130 line:80%
come here for the market.

00:30:01.130 --> 00:30:02.610 line:80%
Come and see, everyone.

00:30:03.090 --> 00:30:05.980 line:80%
These are weapons
passed down for generations.

00:30:05.980 --> 00:30:07.660 line:80%
Today, I sell them at a low price.

00:30:07.660 --> 00:30:08.780 line:80%
Don't miss this chance.

00:30:08.780 --> 00:30:09.700 line:80%
Make way.

00:30:09.700 --> 00:30:10.453 line:80%
Passers-by,

00:30:10.464 --> 00:30:11.410 line:80%
don't miss this chance.

00:30:11.420 --> 00:30:12.500 line:80%
Sir,

00:30:12.500 --> 00:30:14.530 line:80%
lend me your stall for a day.

00:30:14.530 --> 00:30:15.370 line:80%
How do I lend it?

00:30:15.370 --> 00:30:16.800 line:80%
Fortune telling!

00:30:16.800 --> 00:30:18.240 line:80%
Always accurate!

00:30:20.330 --> 00:30:21.810 line:80%
Then I'll throw in another day.

00:30:21.810 --> 00:30:22.700 line:80%
Small trinkets!

00:30:22.700 --> 00:30:24.020 line:80%
Goodbye.

00:30:25.003 --> 00:30:26.696 line:80%
This is not a place
that sells persimmons.

00:30:27.330 --> 00:30:28.370 line:80%
Why rent it?

00:30:28.500 --> 00:30:29.806 line:80%
You want to eat more persimmons?

00:30:30.500 --> 00:30:32.220 line:80%
You are about to become one yourself.

00:30:34.460 --> 00:30:35.300 line:80%
This time,

00:30:36.700 --> 00:30:37.940 line:80%
we try another way.

00:30:40.220 --> 00:30:42.050 line:80%
(Sunshine Blade)
Everyone, come and see.

00:30:42.530 --> 00:30:44.890 line:80%
This Sunshine Blade
was left by an elder.

00:30:44.890 --> 00:30:46.530 line:80%
If not for lacking travel funds,

00:30:46.530 --> 00:30:48.330 line:80%
I'd never sell it cheap.

00:30:48.740 --> 00:30:50.290 line:80%
Don't miss this chance.

00:30:50.740 --> 00:30:51.890 line:80%
Passers-by,

00:30:51.890 --> 00:30:53.180 line:80%
don't miss this chance.

00:30:57.180 --> 00:30:58.570 line:80%
Why is no one interested?

00:31:02.460 --> 00:31:03.300 line:80%
Zhao,

00:31:03.500 --> 00:31:04.933 line:80%
if your aunt knew

00:31:04.944 --> 00:31:06.397 line:80%
you were selling her blade like this,

00:31:06.740 --> 00:31:08.180 line:80%
would she burst from her coffin?

00:31:11.220 --> 00:31:12.700 line:80%
Was it not your bad idea?

00:31:14.530 --> 00:31:15.610 line:80%
Tell me.

00:31:15.610 --> 00:31:16.780 line:80%
Can this really lure

00:31:16.780 --> 00:31:18.500 line:80%
Uncle Shi out?

00:31:18.500 --> 00:31:19.500 line:80%
Even in seclusion,

00:31:20.570 --> 00:31:22.290 line:80%
they still need daily supplies.

00:31:22.570 --> 00:31:23.700 line:80%
And I have asked around.

00:31:23.700 --> 00:31:24.680 line:80%
The Shi family is large.

00:31:25.460 --> 00:31:26.850 line:80%
They must buy many things.

00:31:28.020 --> 00:31:29.370 line:80%
By reason,

00:31:29.370 --> 00:31:30.700 line:80%
they should come out

00:31:30.700 --> 00:31:32.180 line:80%
to restock every month.

00:31:36.370 --> 00:31:37.500 line:80%
Let me have a look.

00:31:41.180 --> 00:31:42.020 line:80%
Here.

00:31:48.370 --> 00:31:50.130 line:80%
The blade looks sharp.

00:31:50.420 --> 00:31:51.260 line:80%
I'll test it.

00:31:53.660 --> 00:31:54.780 line:80%
Sir, to be honest,

00:31:55.130 --> 00:31:56.890 line:80%
this blade is best for cutting pork.

00:31:56.890 --> 00:31:58.090 line:80%
It has slaughtered

00:31:58.090 --> 00:32:00.330 line:80%
many animals.

00:32:03.610 --> 00:32:04.890 line:80%
It may be ugly,

00:32:05.780 --> 00:32:06.620 line:80%
but

00:32:07.090 --> 00:32:08.610 line:80%
it cuts meat well enough.

00:32:08.610 --> 00:32:09.700 line:80%
How is my blade ugly?

00:32:11.090 --> 00:32:12.220 line:80%
You have good eyes, sir.

00:32:12.660 --> 00:32:14.530 line:80%
Though this is a precious blade,

00:32:14.530 --> 00:32:15.610 line:80%
the price is not high.

00:32:16.180 --> 00:32:17.020 line:80%
How much?

00:32:17.700 --> 00:32:18.540 line:80%
100,000 taels.

00:32:19.430 --> 00:32:20.290 line:80%
How much?

00:32:20.290 --> 00:32:21.130 line:80%
100,000 taels.

00:32:22.940 --> 00:32:24.370 line:80%
Have you two gone mad for money?

00:32:24.850 --> 00:32:26.020 line:80%
Swindlers.

00:32:27.090 --> 00:32:28.220 line:80%
You wasted my time.

00:33:10.500 --> 00:33:11.340 line:80%
Strange.

00:33:12.130 --> 00:33:13.330 line:80%
Where did he go?

00:33:24.220 --> 00:33:25.130 line:80%
So high.

00:33:49.530 --> 00:33:50.500 line:80%
Nie Zhe is more impatient

00:33:50.500 --> 00:33:51.740 line:80%
than I thought.

00:33:52.020 --> 00:33:53.130 line:80%
Their positions are unusual.

00:33:53.980 --> 00:33:54.973 line:80%
Be careful of formations.

00:34:44.660 --> 00:34:45.780 line:80%
They are here for me.

00:34:46.100 --> 00:34:46.940 line:80%
I'll hold them off.

00:34:47.180 --> 00:34:48.020 line:80%
You go.

00:34:49.679 --> 00:34:50.879 line:80%
(Qian position, Kun position.)

00:34:51.220 --> 00:34:53.140 line:80%
(Why does it resemble
the Big Dipper Formation?)

00:35:02.140 --> 00:35:02.980 line:80%
Go.

00:35:19.720 --> 00:35:30.380 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

